 - [%as:]: added missing args param for local dbs
 - [%as:]: fixed missing assert_user_permissions() method in some result dbs
 - [%as:]: fixed mongita using some weird attributes
 - [%as:]: fixed tinydb not accepting user param
 - [%as:]: create_job_from_id is no longer restricted
 - [%as:]: fixed schema for queues
 - [%as:]: fixed other lingering references
 - [%as:]: fixed wrong import for SINGLE_USER in database
 - [%as:]: fixed slurm squeue limited to current user only
 - [%as:]: fixed slurm cache always missing
 - [%as:]: added missing account option
 - [%as:]: updated lingering references
 - [%as:]: fixed weird error handling in license info program
 - [%as:]: fixed swapped host for local and non local servers
 - [%as:]: fixed using wrong firestore db in tests
 - [%as:]: fixed crash in job endpoint when streaming an empty file
 - [%as:]: fixed wrong server settings type in api
 - [%as:]: better handling for server reloading in config save
 - [%as:]: fixed locking style sometimes not being correctly set to lockf
 - [%as:]: fixed jobs
 - [%as:]: fixed user auth not working after adding support for safe_access
 - [%as:]: fixed 500 errors when user dir does not exist yet
 - [%as:]: fixed failing to parse Orca Censo calculations with solvents
 - [%as:]: builds for CentOS-7.9 no longer have batoms (which is unavailable) set as the default rendering engine
 - [%as:]: added missing stderr redirect for PBS

